<p>
Sometimes you get “Video Not Supported”
</p>

<p>
2 possible solutions: add &#039;double&#039; to the bottom of your config.cfg, or, if that doesn&#039;t help, use &#039;windowed&#039;.
</p>

<p>
It could also be an X configuration thing: I fixed it by fixing my sync rate to 75hz…
</p>
